casebody.data:
DART CHEROKEE BASIN OPERATING COMPANY, LLC, et al., petitioners,
v.
Brandon W. OWENS. No. 13-719. Supreme Court of the United States April 7, 2014.

Motion of Chamber of Commerce of the United States of America for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Tenth Circuit granted.
